description:
Mike's Gang Again
Once in a while Dink has a friend with him who films the sessions with a second camera. Dink's video buddy was right there when they filmed the four squids in the first session so what we've done is to include this second camera footage as a bonus at the end of the tape. The action is the same as the first session, but you'll see it from a different angle and you might see something that you missed the first time around. In any case, you are sure to enjoy it again as much as you did the first time.
title: Alberto, Alex, Mike, & Myers
